<li id="cite_note-11"><b><a href="#cite_ref-11" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.MolecularAssembler.com/KSRM/2.1.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.MolecularAssembler.com/KSRM/2.1.htm" rel="nofollow">2.1</a></li>
